"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"Donald Trump won the Republican primary in South Carolina with 60% of the vote. Nikki Haley, the former governor, was not favored by the electors. She warned against making the wrong choices, predicting that Trump would not defeat Joe Biden.\",            \"english_title\": \"Politics\",            \"translated_version\": \"Donald Trump gan\u00f3 la primaria republicana en Carolina del Sur con el 60% de los votos. Nikki Haley, la ex gobernadora, no fue la favorita de los electores. Advirti\u00f3 sobre tomar decisiones equivocadas, prediciendo que Trump no vencer\u00eda a Joe Biden.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Politics\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"ECOWAS lifted sanctions on Niger after Mohamed Bazoum, the president, was toppled in a military coup. The sanctions were removed due to humanitarian concerns and to discourage plans of leaving the bloc by the junta and neighboring countries.\",            \"english_title\": \"Politics\",            \"translated_version\": \"ECOWAS levant\u00f3 las sanciones a N\u00edger despu\u00e9s de que Mohamed Bazoum, el presidente, fuera derrocado en un golpe militar. Las sanciones se levantaron debido a preocupaciones humanitarias y para desalentar los planes de salir del bloque por parte de la junta y los pa\u00edses vecinos.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Politics\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Western leaders visited Kyiv to show support for Ukraine on the anniversary of Russia's invasion. Ursula von der Leyen and other leaders pledged Europe's financial, economic, military, and moral support until Ukraine is free.\",            \"english_title\": \"Politics\",            \"translated_version\": \"L\u00edderes occidentales visitaron Kyiv para mostrar apoyo a Ucrania en el aniversario de la invasi\u00f3n de Rusia. Ursula von der Leyen y otros l\u00edderes prometieron el apoyo financiero, econ\u00f3mico, militar y moral de Europa hasta que Ucrania sea libre.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Politics\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Warren Buffett of Berkshire Hathaway warned of declining performance for his firm. He mentioned a lack of attractive deals and a record high cash pile of $167.6bn last quarter.\",            \"english_title\": \"Economy\",            \"translated_version\": \"Warren Buffett de Berkshire Hathaway advirti\u00f3 sobre el rendimiento decreciente de su empresa. Mencion\u00f3 la falta de ofertas atractivas y una acumulaci\u00f3n r\u00e9cord de efectivo de $167.6bn el \u00faltimo trimestre.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Economy\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Heathrow airport in London abandoned plans for a third runway. The new boss aims to accommodate more passengers without expanding the airport's footprint.\",            \"english_title\": \"Business\",            \"translated_version\": \"El aeropuerto de Heathrow en Londres abandon\u00f3 los planes para una tercera pista. El nuevo jefe tiene como objetivo acomodar a m\u00e1s pasajeros sin expandir la huella del aeropuerto.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Business\"        }    ]}"